A vertically oriented parchment-style poster with ornate medieval manuscript borders, navy-and-gold corner emblems, and eight numbered instructional panels arranged in a two-column grid. The panels mix small schematic diagrams, icons, arrows, and symbolic figures: boundaries, circles, signal waves, an eye, a heart, a blood drop, a chalice, a serpent, a shield, and monk-like illuminated figures. The palette is cream, navy, gold, black, and dark red, with serif small-caps typography and rubric-style emphasis, ending in a bottom “distinction loop” flow diagram.
